<h1 class="mb-5">Work</h1>
<p>Below are some examples of my work I've had the pleasure of being apart of.</p>
<p>They're a selection of both client projects and personal projects that have helped expand my knowledge.</p>
<div class="my-5 grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        {%- for project in projects.projects -%}
        <article class="flex flex-col text-base text-center">
            {% image project.image, "", "Maid About Town homepage screenshot",
            "(min-width: 1024px) 500px, 100vw" %}
            <span class="mt-5 font-semibold underline">{{ project.title }}</span>
            <span class="mt-5">{{project.description}}</span>
            <span class="mt-5">Tech stack: {{project.stack}}</span>
            <a href={{project.internalUrl}} class="mt-5">View case study &rarr;</a>
        </article>
        {%- endfor -%}
</div>